subtitleNullable: This is the CKPlus dtaset but I removed the duplicated from all the classes
descriptionNullable:
This dataset will be used to train the emotion detection model

This CKPlus dataset contains 981 images from 7 emotion classes:

- anger (135 images)
- contempt (54 images)
- disgust (177 images)
- fear (75 images)
- happy (207 images)
- sadness (84 images)
- surprise (249 images)

Each image is in grey scale and has fixed size of 48*48.

The original Dataset can be downloaded [here](https://www.kaggle.com/shawon10/ckplus)
